pageContext.claim: “Her district is so filthy dirty. It’s filthy dirty with all of the things, I won't say it, but the needles and everything else. These are areas that were, 10 years ago, the best in the country and now they're disgusting. She [Nancy Pelosi] ought to spend more time back in San Francisco taking care of her community, instead of wasting everybody’s time.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump routinely trashes cities run by Democratic politicians. In reality, San Francisco consistently rates among the most beautiful cities in America. But the president has a long-running feud with House Speaker Nancy Pelosi, whose congressional district overlaps with the city.
